channel.title: Server not online?
channel.description:
I owned my own server about a year ago and im just now returning back to my server but with a different source l port forwarded, set variables correctly, have my no-ip host and im running run.bat perfectly fine, l can even login to it as owner but, when l try and post my server to mopar status page...it says
" Error: The server ReallyWaterfrontPk is offline, it must be online before you can register it here. "
How can l put it online? how can l solve this?
